Vegan Silk Saree Is a plant Based Silk 

Why Vegan Silk?
1. Cruelty Free - no silkworm killed or tortured during the process

2. Plant Based Silk - The silk is obtained from Plant Based Fiber ( Wood Pulp )

3. Budget Friendly - Vegan Silk is Budget friendly and Affordable Compared to Silk. Price Range starts from RM200 and above

4. Easy to drape & Lightweight - Vegan Silk is certainly Very very lightweight, breathable fabric as made from plant based fiber & most importantly , The pleats falla easily! You dont have to pre pleats or iron the pleats

5. Can be gifted to Bridesman Or Mappilai Tholan As its Budget Friendly

This new year began with a good start for me being a part of South Indian Best Makeup Artist competition. Unlike masterclasses where I get to meet makeup artists as my students, Urchava creations got me an opportunity to interact and share my nitty-gritty of makeup with the fellow makeup artists in the competition. And not to forget that failure always paves way to success. So those who couldn’t win the competition should pat themselves back and keep going towards your milestone and so the winners too without settling down with one victory! All thanks to @urchava_creations for arranging this wonderful makeup competition and for opening the gate to many more opportunities for many makeup artists. I am so glad to be a part of this event and much thanks to all who worked behind this event!!!

There must be times we would think of appreciating or thanking someone! Likewise, I’ve come across many lovely souls in my life and I’m always grateful for them. Now I take this moment to convey my hearty thanks to one such lovely soul from Angels, Chennai @angels.egmore Every time I visit Chennai for the makeup classes, he never failed to give his contribution involuntarily with zero expectations in return. He just reads our mind, understands our needs and spontaneously arrange everything right away. Despite his background, his modesty always surprises and I always admire about it. I couldn’t find a word another word than thanks, to show my gratefulness!!! Thank you so much brother Vishnu !!!

Good afternoon y’all! 🤩

Yesterday was one such beautiful day where I felt the same I was before 5, 6 years ago. The student phase where I eagerly attend all my Guru @kannanraajamanickam  sir’s classes with more eagerness and hell lot of curiosity to groom my skills! 🙌🏻

It was a get together that was arranged for all his students. It felt like a huge community all getting together at a single place! It was one such event which I would cherish for my life time! ✨

My inner being felt like Sridevi as she was 5,6 years back with the same enthusiasm to learn but being in comfortable and happy zone! 🥹  for which I’m forever grateful for my Guru. 

The get together was awesome! I met so many Makeup Artists and friends all at a time under the same roof. Had a good time dancing and sharing our knowledge with one another! 

A Guru is a guru! No matter what and who you are! He doesn’t want us to get back to our places without getting some valuable input along with a makeover demo! He shared his knowledge and ideas on how to grow our business to the next level and level ourselves up! 🥹🙌🏻

When people say, I’m such a good teacher where only very few can be, I felt like how much my Guru has incorporated his skills & characters inside me. I felt so happy & proud that I could be atleast a percent as a better person he always wanted his students to be! 🩷

As a guru, yesterday I understood that what a healthy and beautiful community he has built. A community of people with 0% ego & 100% generous & kind to each other. As a entrepreneur, I totally forgot to pamper & take care of myself and this was one such day that made me realised that how much my happiness and peace of mind matters! 😇

To sum up, I was over the moon and this event felt like a time travel experience which is more better as I’m the same individual with the love, respect, curiosity to learn but at a better place and with own identity and establishments! 🥹❤️

Thank you for this memorable day Guru and thank you for the all the valuable experiences which I should incorporate to become a better version of myself professionally and personally! 😇✨

Special thanks to @durgadevigopalan for capturing this ♥️

Kannan Raajamanickam Master-

People who see him as a Makeup Artist might see his extra-ordinary Talent but, Only his students can relate to his Golden heart. One of the purest souls!! 
WHAT IMPRESSES ME IS, Today, in the world of Social Media, with so much of noises & ego going around Master is someone where i did see ZERO EGO! 
ZERO ATTITUDE! SO FORGIVING! And He wants his students to be the same! 
He not just preaches which everybody does. He follows what he preaches!!

Apart from the technical knowledge in Makeup, he has taught me the outlook of life. How to be happy, How to be contented, how to be grounded and how not to be. 

Whenever i hear him coming to India, i start getting anxious of what to do, how to surprise him, rather.. how to show my love and gratitude to my master. 
With much health concerns,  i did a Dance Performance in the event which was after a whole of 5 Years! And to my happiness everybody loved and congratulated me which boosted me even more to come out of my cocoon. 

I know my body wasnt in shape, i know my health wasnt too good, yet I WANTED to dance and i danced after a whole of 5 years.. just for you master❣️

Everytime i meet him, i get to change something within me for the betterment of myself. This time too, you had given me a lot of advices personally which i have started to follow already and professionally too, im sure i will make you proud in the near future❣️
I Love you Master. Not just me, all of your precious students will love you forever.
As you always say, yes we are all One Family and we have already started loving each other❣️

Happy Sunday fam! ✨

I hope you would’ve get to know that we’re out of India celebrating our Guru’s Birthday! 🤩 These are the days that I actually live for... 

It was such a great get together and we all his students celebrated it so well with lots of happiness and took so much of memories through this! 🩷

We just had an idea of forecasting how we celebrate his birthday in 2064 and ended up creating this as a video and thought why not sharing this with you all??!! 😊

While thinking about celebrating it 40years later and ended up that he’ll be getting old each year is something doesn’t felt so happy! But what made me feel so good is, even after 40years we all get together and celebrate his birthday even more better! 🙌🏻 

Everyone here in this video are his students. His dedication, love and care towards his students is so precious. Why I love him so much as a Guru is the way he loves us without any intention of getting anything back! 🥺

The way he created us as a community of Makeup Artists is  so inspiring and healthy. And the way we as students of our Guru @kannanraajamanickam is something beyond special... ☺

Years may pass, the unstable things such as money and beauty can pass too. But the love and Companionship we people hold together is entangled and wouldn’t be seperated at any cost and at all times! 🥹🩷

And yes fam, this is the thing I really wanted to convey y’all! Whatever may be our standards, needs, status and more... But at the end of the day, at the end of some period, only love and companionship can sail this boat called life! 🙌🏻

Whatever hard times you are facing now is not permanent, the happiness we feel around us is something unstable and needs so much efforts to continue. But the love we have from our close circle is what always makes us feel so special. Experience the blessing called love from the persons you have!✨

Love them! Cherish them! At last what we can take with us is  just love and memories! 🥹❤️

With love, 
Sridevi Thiyagarajan 💛

Part 1

As the room filled with laughter and excitement I couldn’t help but feel a wave of nostalgia wash over me. 

My friends and loved ones had gone above and beyond to make this day unforgettable. They had meticulously planned every detail ensuring that each surprise brought a smile to my face. From the games and activities to the thoughtful gifts they had truly captured the essence of my inner child.

As the party kicked off we immersed ourselves in a whirlwind of laughter and friendly competition. The air was filled with the sounds of jovial conversations and the occasional burst of laughter.

As the party drew to a close I couldn’t help but feel overwhelmed with gratitude. The effort my friends and loved ones had put into celebrating my birthday left me feeling immensely blessed. This was not just a celebration of another year added to my life but a testament to the enduring power of friendship love and the joy of reliving cherished memories.

this birthday would forever hold a special place in my soul. It had brought back my childhood memories.

✨ Grateful for an unforgettable journey through Europe ✨

Recently, I had the incredible privilege of exploring the stunning beauty of Europe. From the picturesque landscapes to the serene nature, every moment felt like a dream. I can’t help but feel like I was born again to witness the breathtaking wonders this world has to offer. 

Thank you, God, for your endless grace upon me. Every step I took, every sight I beheld, left me mesmerized and in awe of your creation. My soul was truly stuck in those enchanting places, and today, as I head back to my country, I can’t help but feel a longing to return.

As I reflect and reminisce on the memories made, I will forever treasure the sights that took my breath away, the moments that filled my heart with joy, and the beauty that touched my soul. Europe, you will always have a special place in my heart.

Until we meet again... ❤️🌍
